DESCRIPTION:Southwest Airlines is hosting a virtual info session to share more about our Junior Technology Associate Program (JTAP)\, application tips & tricks\, and what to expect during our application process. Join us on Wednesday\, May 13 from 12:00 - 1:00 p.m. CT to learn about the program\, hear what participants can expect\, and get your questions answered. Register today to attend!
